reviewText:
Wonderful video heavy information , right to the point , well done , I would recommend '
this video to every one as they will learn what is really going on in the world as well as
in the bible the things we have missed in our own studying .The best of Dr. Leonard Horowitz..

A well presented perspective. Two problems in the first half. The pics of healing water are not of water but ICE. The second error is in using base nine for these new tools. The correct mathmatics as will be proven soon is base 12. When applied correctly it will solve all of modern sciences pitfalls.
So grateful to see this info (from the book) now available on video, especially by Dr. Leonard Horowitz himself. Everyone needs to watch this.
Based on the best-selling book by Dr. Leonard Horowitz, author of Emerging Viruses and over 10 best-selling books. Horowitz never disappoints!
Heavy book. Not for the faint of heart. But for those seeking the truth Dr Horowitz had done so much research and has thought provoking lessons to be learned! Thank you Sir!
